  <subsection xml:id="subsec-converting-units-of-speed">
    <title>Converting units of speed.</title>
    <introduction>
      <p>
      Speed can be converted from kilometre per hour<m>(km/h)</m> to 
      metres per second<m>(m/s)</m> and also metres per second<m>(m/s)</m> to 
      kilometre per hour<m>(km/h)</m>.
    </p>
